name: Showdown between Woody and The Prospector
name_original: Showdown between Woody and The Prospector
description: this game reminds me of toy story 2. the controls are w, a, s, d controls Woody. To shoot with Woody press the space bar. the controls for the Prospector are the number pads 4, 5, 6, 8.  To shoot with the Prospector press num pad 9.
